{"tid":1534324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點攞太子站 831 CCTV (有D長)","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:43:36.000Z","uid":290512,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"44311adc58c519200cfe1132be5d57faf906f7a8","tid":1534324,"uid":290512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:24:57.000Z","msg":"有好幾個 post 都有講點樣攞太子站嘅 CCTV, 我分享下我嘅睇法<br />\n<br />\n我應為最直接嘅方法係由太子站嘅傷者以<span style=\"color: red;\">傳訊令狀</span> (Writ of Summons)方式開展一個<span style=\"color: red;\">人身傷亡訴訟</span> (Personal Injury case)。  由傷者去做嘅原因係因為佢地會有權利 (Standing) 去提出訴訟，而一般人會需要額外證明同案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n人身傷亡訴訟嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">被告</span>應該有2個。 <span style=\"color: red;\">1) 黨鐵 2) Popo</span><br />\n<br />\n告<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span>嘅訴因 (Cause of action) 係根據香港法例第314章《佔用人法律責任條例》第3條，即佔用人﹙即<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵﹚違反一般謹慎責任</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，告<span style=\"color: red;\">popo</span> 嘅訴因可以係<span style=\"color: red;\">襲擊 (Battery)</span>或者<span style=\"color: red;\">非法禁錮 (False imprisonment)</span>，當然傷者係需要證明 popo 當時唔係執行緊職務。 請參考<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/警員執行職務和過分武力/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=2e2a7ab2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%2F&h=f1d6a558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/警員執行職務和過分武力/</a> ﹙將來亦可以申請要求popo提供打人嘅狗嘅名同埋編號﹚<br />\n<br />\n係人身傷亡訴訟下面有<span style=\"color: red;\">3個方法攞CCTV</span>。  方法1：當送達 (Serve)傳訊令狀之後，請馬上根據香港法例第4A章《高等法院規則》第24(7)條或者香港法例第336H章《區域法院規則》第24(7)條出一個<span style=\"color: red;\">要求「作出特定文件的透露命令」 (Specific discovery) 嘅傳票 (Summons)申請</span>，並加上一份誓章 (Affirmation) 作為證據，要求提供太子站嘅 CCTV。  呢個係最正路嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n方法2﹙需要高級法律撚俾意見﹚：出<span style=\"color: red;\">禁制令 (Injunction) 阻止黨鐵銷毀太子831 CCTV</span>，然之後慢慢再問佢攞。<br />\n<br />\n方法3﹙需要高級法律撚，因為我純粹睇書未做過﹚：出 <span style=\"color: red;\">Anton Piller Order</span>。 重點係 Anton Piller Order 係<span style=\"color: red;\">可以由原告人單方面提出 (ex parte)</span>。  請參考<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/commencement_of_trial/q8.shtml。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FcivilCase%2Fcommencement_of_trial%2Fq8.shtml%E3%80%82&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=857be963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/commencement_of_trial/q8.shtml。</a><br />\n<br />\n以上所有方法都要儘快出，<span style=\"color: red;\">建議傷者揾義務律師或者政黨律師搞</span>。 你預搞好所有文件都要1至2個星期，仲未計要排去審。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫推，我P牌推唔到。"},{"pid":"21a3f282d96830b9a2963301fdca3280fe10e8e1","tid":1534324,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54abaa672b15e0dcf05000a98979df62869cff2d","tid":1534324,"uid":141057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"072f998a30d4cca6082717aa74c6b54ea9e4d4bf","tid":1534324,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e18fc32cd1f51a8e9f684ddfde48188d8819b07","tid":1534324,"uid":288442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:26:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7878516ac25cf1b86afdeb1902dd1a591be1b1f7","tid":1534324,"uid":288442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df71eeb9937542bb8dcb19af275467360f4a7f52","tid":1534324,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b84d2ced7ec524f28949ae960ac424758a254c3","tid":1534324,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"搵泛民大狀出手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ee6d77e24357012dba4caceb8fa1fea8b060c5","tid":1534324,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e950b3e9b904ef3feb0d89c358166efe2c8db9","tid":1534324,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5187f3ee162487615c1216851a2f1bf0fc13c868","tid":1534324,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaBbTAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaBbTAC.png&h=2beb762c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辛苦一眾考官7號要幫機場重考</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e9781f121dc3ff048694ed1fb428fab8c8b994","tid":1534324,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa6aa7ab65be220d7730a4f4ce8c5163464d5c0","tid":1534324,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"推！831傷者請入！"},{"pid":"52fbd4bbcaafd9d1921777e4853537dfa198d0b2","tid":1534324,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:31:30.000Z","msg":"8.31傷者快d上水"},{"pid":"b63016c4fb7ca43676d627df9fe8efa9ca8cfc14","tid":1534324,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04a4c3465fd8adff92dfa08b58e1d42376b3ea23","tid":1534324,"uid":288372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:34:31.000Z","msg":"推！上國際法庭最好"},{"pid":"549929db03724d3b5af5c07018a277e23d7801ee","tid":1534324,"uid":46447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e351f318419471112b39cc939773b36ee5f4b25","tid":1534324,"uid":224219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee62adb78614639f7f534ea4419aaaad65ea0acf","tid":1534324,"uid":189068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cp1CShj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCp1CShj.png&h=9b9ab569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCQsuqZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCQsuqZ.png&h=48aa381c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6001645378eb86cfbd59064e379fbeadbca9ad92","tid":1534324,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵者，詭道也。故能而示之不能，用而示之不用，近而示之遠，遠而示之近。利而誘之，亂而取之，實而備之，強而避之，怒而撓之，卑而驕之，佚而勞之，親而離之，攻其不備，出其不意。此兵家之勝，不可先傳也。</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>兵者詭道也</strong><br />\n用兵之道在於千變萬化<br />\n<strong>能而示之不能，用而示之不用</strong><br />\n隱藏真正的實力或者是讓不欲人知的訊息隱藏不露<br />\n<strong>近而示之遠，遠而示之近</strong><br />\n將主力或即將要發動的攻勢，佯裝到錯誤的距離及位置，令敵人評估失準<br />\n<strong>利而誘之</strong><br />\n用利益引誘貪利之人<br />\n<strong>亂而取之</strong><br />\n製造混亂，然後再乘虛而入<br />\n<strong>實而備之</strong><br />\n以充足的準備，去面對軍隊整齊有實力的對手<br />\n<strong>強而避之</strong><br />\n對強大士氣旺盛的敵人，先避其鋒，待其疲憊，再尋求反擊的機會<br />\n<strong>怒而撓之</strong><br />\n不斷騷擾敵人，令其破綻百出<br />\n<strong>卑而驕之</strong><br />\n以卑微的態度，令自大的對手失去危機感<br />\n<strong>佚而勞之</strong><br />\n以逸待勞，以最佳狀態迎接奔波疲勞的敵人<br />\n<strong>親而離之</strong><br />\n接近敵人的親信，然後進行離間行為，令其內外孤立<br />\n<strong>攻其不備</strong><br />\n攻擊對手無防備，或較薄弱的地方<br />\n<strong>出其不意</strong><br />\n在對手意想不到的地方及情勢下發動攻擊<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"faf798a3d117ee4d5d7780c90e3f6e6cfbb4d77a","tid":1534324,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c20fae29cdc1ddd784c8142d19b8320b0150f4","tid":1534324,"uid":300536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"出得writ黎都拜山，pre-action discovery 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOcjpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOcjpS</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"51da3aacb423b3e8a346e61b543d7e18eeabcea5","tid":1534324,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da850b0df8b427a25530c38e88bde9363c6e90d7","tid":1534324,"uid":209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n希望受害手足出黎行多一步"},{"pid":"a091497ef6bc116c6ecf5b6010677a0d3c84ff77","tid":1534324,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2be0bbc89e5db0277445c83add9634a6187444db","tid":1534324,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8422c1e76048f066adb7b7733f081a33a470a57f","tid":1534324,"uid":290512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c20fae29cdc1ddd784c8142d19b8320b0150f4","tid":1534324,"uid":300536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"出得writ黎都拜山，pre-action discovery 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOcjpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOcjpS</a></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:44:06.000Z","msg":"求其整個 general endorsement 即出 specific discovery 唔會花太多時間<br />\n<br />\n但係同意 pre-action discovery 都係一個方法，2個方法都係要整 affirmation 冇咩分別。"},{"pid":"e9b119a53001680a0c7c78c7850970b4ae8603ef","tid":1534324,"uid":274247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"