:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:04:59.000Z","msg":"呢個真係可以做<br />\n外國就算起完條橋空氣污染搞到居民健康都會集體告<br />\n呢件事仲要直接人身傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088bb7f1c477ba775fbe50158390b32b4da400c4","tid":1534324,"uid":141057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:03.000Z","msg":"推呀 但香港好似冇得集體訴訟"},{"pid":"81d996cc67a9198f2d70a1e0259e3e98b9fb4d74","tid":1534324,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e59b6f51c079f237ea934767b4b6e1d92aec4051","tid":1534324,"uid":184671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44311adc58c519200cfe1132be5d57faf906f7a8","tid":1534324,"uid":290512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:24:57.000Z","msg":"有好幾個 post 都有講點樣攞太子站嘅 CCTV, 我分享下我嘅睇法<br />\n<br />\n我應為最直接嘅方法係由太子站嘅傷者以<span style=\"color: red;\">傳訊令狀</span> (Writ of Summons)方式開展一個<span style=\"color: red;\">人身傷亡訴訟</span> (Personal Injury case)。  由傷者去做嘅原因係因為佢地會有權利 (Standing) 去提出訴訟，而一般人會需要額外證明同案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n人身傷亡訴訟嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">被告</span>應該有2個。 <span style=\"color: red;\">1) 黨鐵 2) Popo</span><br />\n<br />\n告<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span>嘅訴因 (Cause of action) 係根據香港法例第314章《佔用人法律責任條例》第3條，即佔用人﹙即<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵﹚違反一般謹慎責任</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，告<span style=\"color: red;\">popo</span> 嘅訴因可以係<span style=\"color: red;\">襲擊 (Battery)</span>或者<span style=\"color: red;\">非法禁錮 (False imprisonment)</span>，當然傷者係需要證明 popo 當時唔係執行緊職務。 請參考<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/警員執行職務和過分武力/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=2e2a7ab2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%2F&h=f1d6a558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/警員執行職務和過分武力/</a> ﹙將來亦可以申請要求popo提供打人嘅狗嘅名同埋編號﹚<br />\n<br />\n係人身傷亡訴訟下面有<span style=\"color: red;\">3個方法攞CCTV</span>。  方法1：當送達 (Serve)傳訊令狀之後，請馬上根據香港法例第4A章《高等法院規則》第24(7)條或者香港法例第336H章《區域法院規則》第24(7)條出一個<span style=\"color: red;\">要求「作出特定文件的透露命令」 (Specific discovery) 嘅傳票 (Summons)申請</span>，並加上一份誓章 (Affirmation) 作為證據，要求提供太子站嘅 CCTV。  呢個係最正路嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n方法2﹙需要高級法律撚俾意見﹚：出<span style=\"color: red;\">禁制令 (Injunction) 阻止黨鐵銷毀太子831 CCTV</span>，然之後慢慢再問佢攞。<br />\n<br />\n方法3﹙需要高級法律撚，因為我純粹睇書未做過﹚：出 <span style=\"color: red;\">Anton Piller Order</span>。 重點係 Anton Piller Order 係<span style=\"color: red;\">可以由原告人單方面提出 (ex parte)</span>。  請參考<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/commencement_of_trial/q8.shtml。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FcivilCase%2Fcommencement_of_trial%2Fq8.shtml%E3%80%82&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=857be963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/civilCase/commencement_of_trial/q8.shtml。</a><br />\n<br />\n以上所有方法都要儘快出，<span style=\"color: red;\">建議傷者揾義務律師或者政黨律師搞</span>。 你預搞好所有文件都要1至2個星期，仲未計要排去審。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫推，我P牌推唔到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"最簡單係出endorsement of writ ，同時出ex parter injunction, preservation order唔俾佢delete先<br />\n<br />\n但係都係好似琴晚咁講，要有人出黎做plaintiff"},{"pid":"c1540bb22a1265db36f3103837830298c8fa4b78","tid":1534324,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d155c4cc349198cb4dae366fceaebb31ee2224de","tid":1534324,"uid":184671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"漏左，preservation order係ex parte同urgent做<br />\n<br />\n夠人手幫手，一兩日已出到"},{"pid":"fda23a19e5c3f7b9aba3571e79ae15b250d45b29","tid":1534324,"uid":284956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"推，希望傷者幫手，還大家一個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ce838337a20ade1fcab97a1a7a253380ca02fd","tid":1534324,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f37910f1d5e5f5b5fa22ec65d3deed7949695fe","tid":1534324,"uid":114798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"cd4e38679e78be81a37f101bdcaba16c02db618c","tid":1534324,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"088bb7f1c477ba775fbe50158390b32b4da400c4","tid":1534324,"uid":141057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:03.000Z","msg":"推呀 但香港好似冇得集體訴訟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"洗乜集體，就算當時喺車撘緊車嘅人無被打一樣可以以驚嚇有精神損失控告，要求金額一蚊都得，重點係保住cctv"},{"pid":"763510547f95576383a568292cc4c68f8b141dc8","tid":1534324,"uid":181521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:38:36.000Z","msg":"908"},{"pid":"70fffbaf4d5d8a4240176502648798b6d442d0b7","tid":1534324,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55e7f26d980086eb742f85c4d28170faa7f4b873","tid":1534324,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d923efc93fb85c3d48d8667398e2b25119563f15","tid":1534324,"uid":127528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"239704d7e20b00d90eccfe4599e1d3a1e8b66b4c","tid":1534324,"uid":58781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f45cbd5ba14a699d29b80f75ab4e342f3ce63d30","tid":1534324,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"437bc63d98057f4a83c23c451dc1937aedd56193","tid":1534324,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"推到當晚在場嘅人見到"},{"pid":"c849d4f275d31ca3359089eb6ebbd7456fa297d6","tid":1534324,"uid":261667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"跪求法律巴出手"},{"pid":"266d438e2992a711ca0f6ee3a70412fac18211f8","tid":1534324,"uid":260549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"183e4b90cfab8a8851e124e760931a43e8c50027","tid":1534324,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵者，詭道也。故能而示之不能，用而示之不用，近而示之遠，遠而示之近。利而誘之，亂而取之，實而備之，強而避之，怒而撓之，卑而驕之，佚而勞之，親而離之，攻其不備，出其不意。此兵家之勝，不可先傳也。</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>兵者詭道也</strong><br />\n用兵之道在於千變萬化<br />\n<strong>能而示之不能，用而示之不用</strong><br />\n隱藏真正的實力或者是讓不欲人知的訊息隱藏不露<br />\n<strong>近而示之遠，遠而示之近</strong><br />\n將主力或即將要發動的攻勢，佯裝到錯誤的距離及位置，令敵人評估失準<br />\n<strong>利而誘之</strong><br />\n用利益引誘貪利之人<br />\n<strong>亂而取之</strong><br />\n製造混亂，然後再乘虛而入<br />\n<strong>實而備之</strong><br />\n以充足的準備，去面對軍隊整齊有實力的對手<br />\n<strong>強而避之</strong><br />\n對強大士氣旺盛的敵人，先避其鋒，待其疲憊，再尋求反擊的機會<br />\n<strong>怒而撓之</strong><br />\n不斷騷擾敵人，令其破綻百出<br />\n<strong>卑而驕之</strong><br />\n以卑微的態度，令自大的對手失去危機感<br />\n<strong>佚而勞之</strong><br />\n以逸待勞，以最佳狀態迎接奔波疲勞的敵人<br />\n<strong>親而離之</strong><br />\n接近敵人的親信，然後進行離間行為，令其內外孤立<br />\n<strong>攻其不備</strong><br />\n攻擊對手無防備，或較薄弱的地方<br />\n<strong>出其不意</strong><br />\n在對手意想不到的地方及情勢下發動攻擊<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"7ce5a7b1ec10285b6814cd048adbcbfbac8568c5","tid":1534324,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62aaa4532e6f433b4b01bc8803453d66b407736c","tid":1534324,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}